Class RiotApi

  • java.lang.Object

    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class RiotApi
extends Object
implements Closeable
    Riot API. The main class for interacting with the Riot API on a low level.

    The EntityApi is simpler and more user-friendly to use.
